# Obsidian config - the brain doubles as an Obsidian vault, and the shared *viewing* posture
# (strict line breaks so hard-wrapped pages flow, reading-view default, delete confirmation,
# raw/ excluded from graph + search) is meant to travel with the brain so it looks the same on
# every device - editing stays the brrain skills' job, never a manual edit. So track the config
# and ignore only the per-device, churny pieces (window/pane layout + caches).
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/cache
